Package de.hsbremen.tc.tnc.message.t.serialize.bytebuffer

Transport byte buffer serialization interfaces.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    TransportReader<T extends TransportData>
    Generic reader, that reads byte data from a byte buffer, and parses it to a transport message object.
    TransportWriter<T extends TransportData>
    Generic writer, that accepts a transport message object and serializes it to the given byte buffer.
